Class Summary
PSSynFeedCategory For Media RSS: Allows a taxonomy to be set that gives an indication of the type of media content, and its particular contents.
PSSynFeedCredit Notable entity and the contribution to the creation of the media object.
PSSynFeedEnclosure Provides a Velocity friendly class for handling enclosures.
PSSynFeedEntry Provides Velocity friendly methods for a Syndication Feed entry.
PSSynFeedImage A Velocity friendly class for a syndication image.
PSSynFeedMediaContent Provides a Velocity friendly wrapper for Media content.
PSSynFeedMediaGroup Velocity friendly wrapper aroound Media Groups.
PSSynFeedProxy Serves as a Velocity friendly proxy class for the underlying syndication libraries.
PSSynFeedRating This allows the permissible audience to be declared.
PSSynFeedRestriction Allows restrictions to be placed on the aggregator rendering the media in the feed.
PSSynFeedThumbnail Allows particular images to be used as representative images for the media object.
